{"tid":2260203,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[藍店]I.T發盈警 料半年虧損擴大至3億　","createTime":"2020-10-27T11:59:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T15:49:55.000Z","uid":266107,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7e79e0b050d31933646c7ee2bd94d66a3e4647f7","tid":2260203,"uid":266107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T11:59:33.000Z","msg":"本地潮牌服飾I.T（999）發盈警，預期公司截至今年8月底止半年將錄得不少於3億的淨虧損，去年同期的淨虧損金額為7,100萬元。<br />\n<br />\n公司指，肺炎疫情導致全球消費者的消費意欲下降，面對異常艱難的營商環境，集團提供額外折扣以刺激銷量。縱然公司於半年業績期間已迅速及果斷採取行動減省成本，然而，所省卻的經營成本不足以抵消銷售和毛利率下降。<br />\n事實上，I.T於今年7月已為截至今年5月底止首季發出盈警，料期內虧損不少於1億元，意味第二財季業績虧損程度比首季惡劣。首個財季不同地區銷售表現均欠佳，其中港澳地區同店銷售按年下跌49.1%，中國下跌11.8%，日本及美國更跌66.1%。整體毛利率按年下跌8.8個百分點至55.1%。<br />\n<br />\nI.T發盈警 料半年虧損擴大至3億　<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201027/642FNTQFYZBZ5HCF2BQ4REXQIQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201027%2F642FNTQFYZBZ5HCF2BQ4REXQIQ%2F&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDBzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=2ee5dd5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201027%2F642FNTQFYZBZ5HCF2BQ4REXQIQ%2F&h=b1fd05ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201027/642FNTQFYZBZ5HCF2BQ4REXQIQ/</a>"},{"pid":"b6c6c144008c23e0d813bcb6aae3cce4f3053e68","tid":2260203,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:00:20.000Z","msg":"豆豆開始下海"},{"pid":"967c8c5c93a9b78d908e883588988461d2e37688","tid":2260203,"uid":240347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6c6c144008c23e0d813bcb6aae3cce4f3053e68","tid":2260203,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:00:20.000Z","msg":"豆豆開始下海"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:00:49.000Z","msg":"佢個女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b54696627b6eb60386867d112c8cd0cc66dcc812","tid":2260203,"uid":266107,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-1